  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. This unit evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors have been assessed; seven factors show achieved levels meeting or exceeding required levels and six previously flagged epistemic gaps have been closed through supplemental Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification and additional bench-top validation campaigns. Decision: Accepted. Note: intended-use scope, patient population, and operating envelope are described in the bound Requirement and Claim nodes rather than in a separate structured Context of Use object.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-requirement",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-cfd-credibility-claim",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/fda-centrifugal-pump-cfd-hemolysis-v3",
  "bindsDataset": [
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/fda-pump-piv-benchmark-dataset",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/hemolysis-in-vitro-experimental-dataset",
    "https://uofa.net/synth/data/monte-carlo-uq-ensemble-dataset"
  ],
