    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed at MRL 5 for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under VAD operating conditions. Achieved levels meet or exceed required levels across all factors. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification confirms NIH prediction within acceptable bounds. Independent analyst review completed without discrepancy. The computational model is judged credible for the intended regulatory submission supporting the Class III VAD device hemolysis safety claim as described in the bound Requirement and Claim nodes.",
